  -----------------------------------------------------------------------
  **Practical connection:** After installing ZAP\'s CA root certificate,
  visit https://juice.shop in Firefox. The padlock appears --- but ZAP\'s
  History tab shows every request and response in plaintext, including
  the Authorization header containing your JWT token. That token grants
  the same access as your password for the duration of the session.
  **Remove the ZAP root certificate from Firefox after the practical.**
  Settings → Privacy & Security → Certificates → View Certificates →
  Authorities → ZAP → Delete.

